scene.message:
Ayase: That's not really{nl}
your fault, teacher.{waitkey}{clearbox}You didn't force it on her,{nl}
right? That Tomomi girl just{nl}
misunderstood.{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Maybe so.{nl}
But{wait_fr:30} I can't say for certain.{waitkey}{clearbox}Maybe, somewhere in my heart,{nl}
I was basking in a sense{nl}
of superiority.{waitkey}{clearbox}Playing the good friend,

{nl}
being kind only on the{nl}
surface.{waitkey}{clearbox}Maybe deep down I didn't{nl}
care at all about how{nl}
Tomomi felt.{waitkey}{clearbox}Maybe I was just drunk on{nl}
being someone who's kind{nl}
to others...{waitkey}and hurting her instead...{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: It's not the{nl}
mask's curse!{nl}
The one who made her like{waitkey}that was...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: We defeated the Snow{nl}
Queen and saved Ms. Saeko,{nl}
yet...{waitkey}the school hasn't returned{nl}
to normal!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: We defeated the Snow{nl}
Queen and saved Ms. Saeko,{nl}
yet...{waitkey}the school is still frozen!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Now that you mention{nl}
it{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}the sky's color is still{nl}
weird, too{waitkey}{ret}

Voice: Hehehe...{waitkey}{nl}
It must be quite cold, hm?{waitkey}{nl}
Ahahaha...{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: The Tomomi within me,{wait_fr:30}{nl}
the Tomomi with human{nl}
weakness, has died. My thanks.{waitkey}{clearbox}I have left my host Tomomi,{nl}
left the vessel that is the{nl}
mask, and become wholly free.{waitkey}{clearbox}Now I become complete.{waitkey}{clearbox}As the complete Night Queen,{nl}
I'll cover this world in the{nl}
white and black of nothing{waitkey}and despair.{waitkey}{ret}
